The Stereo Panoramic Movie Capture plugin for UE4 allows you to capture still images or movies that can then be viewed or played back in stereo giving the illusion that the world is  being rendered in stereoscopic 3D.  In the following sections we will take a look at how to setup and use the Stereo Panoramic Movie Capture plugin and also take a look at how you can create an image viewer inside of UE4 that will allow you to see the images you create in stereo. 


## Starting Out
The Stereo Panoramic Capture How To guide  will walk you through getting your UE4 project setup to be able to capture and view stereo images.

